{\"children\":\"Dog Parks in Wilmington, NC\"}],\"$undefined\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-description\",\"children\":\"Wilmington combines historic riverfront charm with coastal access, offering parks like Empie Park and proximity to dog-friendly beaches.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-rich-description\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Wilmington, NC, is a premier destination for water-loving dogs and their owners. The city features top-tier facilities like the dog park at \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://www.wilmingtonnc.gov/departments/parks-recreation/dog-parks\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Empie Park\"}],null,\", which offers shade and agility equipment. Just a short drive away, the beaches of Wrightsville Beach and Carolina Beach offer seasonal hours for leashed dog walking on the sand. The historic \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"4\",{\"href\":\"https://www.wilmingtonandbeaches.com/things-to-do/attractions/riverwalk/\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Riverwalk\"}],null,\" provides a scenic urban route for socialization along the Cape Fear River. Our \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"7\",{\"href\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/cities/wilmington#park-directory\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Wilmington directory\"}],null,\" serves as a guide to this coastal canine paradise.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"The local culture is heavily influenced by the ocean, but owners must be mindful of seasonal beach rules and heat safety. Wilmington's humid summers make early morning or evening walks best. For visitors needing info on local policies, our \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"/faq\",\"target\":\"$undefined\",\"rel\":\"$undefined\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"FAQ section\"}],null,\" is a helpful resource. The city also hosts a variety of \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"4\",{\"href\":\"/parks-with-bars\",\"target\":\"$undefined\",\"rel\":\"$undefined\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"pet-friendly businesses\"}],null,\" where owners can relax after a day of play. Wilmington’s blend of Southern history and beach life offers an unmatched lifestyle for active dogs.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta-row\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta primary\",\"targetId\":\"park-directory\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-check\"}],\"Browse directory\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta ghost\",\"targetId\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-geo-alt\"}],\"Open map\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/list-your-park\",\"className\":\"hero-cta text-link\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-plus-circle\"}],\"Submit a park\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-footnotes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",\"Data refreshed weekly\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Data refreshed weekly\"]}],[\"$\",\"span\",\"Live availability coming soon\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Live availability coming soon\"]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-visual\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L31\",null,{\"src\":\"/images/cities/wilmington/hero.webp\",\"alt\":\"Wilmington dog park landscape\",\"fill\":true,\"priority\":true,\"sizes\":\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 540px\",\"unoptimized\":true}],\"$L32\"]}]}]]}]}],\"$L33\",\"$L34\",\"$L35\",\"$L36\",\"$L37\",\"$L38\",\"$undefined\",\"$L39\",\"$L3a\",\"$L3b\",\"$L3c\",\"$L3d\"]}]\n2b:[\"$\",\"footer\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-new\",\"chi